300.statusDescription: Redirection: Request has been received, but needs to perform an additional step to complete the request.
statusResolution: Repeat your search to see if the problem persists.

400.statusDescription: Client Error: Request was made by the client, but the request was determined by the server to be not valid.
statusResolution: The requested URI does not represent any resource on the server.
One of the request inputs is out of range.
One of the request inputs is not valid.
A required query parameter was not specified for this request.
One of the query parameters specified in the request URI is not supported.
An invalid value was specified for one of the query parameters in the request URI.

408.statusDescription: Client Error: The client did not produce a request within the time that the server was prepared to wait.
statusResolution: Please ensure your connection to the network is functioning and restart your hardware if necessary
Many times a slow connection causes a delay that prompts the 408 Request Timeout error
Repeat your search to see if the problem persists.

500.statusDescription: Server Error: Valid request was made by the client, but the server failed to complete the request.
statusResolution: Try re-entering your query and clicking the button to repeat your search.
Try reloading from the Home page, and then repeating your search.
Repeat your search to see if the problem persists.
